data.name: richTextBoxHelp.Text
data.value:
Shortcuts on [Script Writer] text box: - Crtl + Shift + 1 ➔ New create template script (empty) - Ctrl + Shift + 2 ➔ New edit template script (empty) - Crtl + Shift + 3 ➔ New create template script (basic) - Ctrl + Shift + 4 ➔ New edit template script (basic) - Ctrl + Shift + S ➔ Submit script, create new meta item when TABLE:'s value is present and the table name does not exist - Ctrl + Shift + D ➔ Delete selected table's script - Ctrl + Shift + Z ➔ Load selected table's script - Ctrl + Shift + C ➔ Compile selected table's script - Ctrl + Shift + P ➔ New paragraph string ///--- - Ctrl + Shift + T ➔ New table name string TABLE: - Ctrl + F ➔ Format/minimize script - Ctrl + Space ➔ Show suggestion box/apply single suggestion
Shortcuts on [Suggestion Box] shown: - Enter/Tab ➔ Apply selected suggestion - Up (on top item) ➔ Exit suggestion box - Down (on script text box) ➔ Enter suggestion box if there is more than one suggestion
